Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.77,0:00:05.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:13.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:33.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.46,0:00:36.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The sound resonates\NInto my heart, so hard and deep
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A field of stars spans endlessly\NAnd through it I carve a passageway
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.32,0:00:42.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In step with time as generations change
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.19,0:00:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Close your eyes and listen closely
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.19,0:00:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shooting stars stream on silently…\Nuntil the goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:50.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep the light inside of you,\Nnever give up don't ever lose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:52.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Transcend time and you will prove,\Nthere is a special place for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.09,0:00:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A blaze of glory is there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.93,0:00:56.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all a part of our estate;\Nlife is our story to create
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.97,0:01:01.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:05.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old by voice of light\NThroughout the age, never fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.54,0:01:09.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A secret fire, a scream of light,\Nvoices calling through twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.29,0:01:11.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cast your thoughts to the wind,\Nhang your wishes on the moon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:13.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Live your life with all your strength\Nfor dreams will reach you very soon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.44,0:01:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your eyes you can see\Nshooting stars up in the night sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.10,0:01:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wishes speak from ages old\Nby voice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.07,0:01:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Throughout the age,\Nnever fade away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.16,0:01:24.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someday your dream will find\Nits place somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.05,0:01:28.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep shining like a star
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.37,0:01:39.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Irregularities detected along\Nwestern perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.30,0:01:41.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Security alert in Areas 3 through 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:42.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Repeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Irregularities detected along\Nwestern perimeter.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:46.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Security alert in Areas 3 through 8!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.58,0:01:49.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.77,0:02:00.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The wall is catching up to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.89,0:02:04.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The place we just ran through\Nis collapsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.54,0:02:07.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you have time to look back,\Nyou have time to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:10.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's all over if the Restrictive Current\Nswallows you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.55,0:02:18.11,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:18.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.01,0:02:21.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The fool!\NIt's that crazy get-up he has on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:21.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.35,0:02:24.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do not use your Zanpaku-to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:26.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The current entangles the spiritual body.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.21,0:02:29.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you use your Zanpaku-to,\Nyou will get caught too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.41,0:02:36.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.75,0:02:37.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:39.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.24,0:02:43.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put me down, Chad!\NI can run on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.87,0:02:49.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.09,0:02:49.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.22,0:03:00.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.99,0:03:06.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Cleaner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:11.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It appears once every seven days!\NAnd this had to be the day!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.98,0:03:15.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, run! It's incredibly fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.70,0:03:20.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! We're close to the exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:26.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.30,0:03:28.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't outrun it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinagiku! Baigon! Lily!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:40.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santen Kesshun! I reject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.43,0:04:03.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is everyone all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.09,0:04:07.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Ichigo!\NThe way you land is so artistic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:09.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.30,0:04:13.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes…\NThat was something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.37,0:04:14.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is more than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.26,0:04:18.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought I'd use\Nmy extra cape so soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:22.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He brought a change of clothes…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.35,0:04:26.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad…\NNo one seems to be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.79,0:04:28.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's there to be glad about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.68,0:04:30.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.25,0:04:33.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Were you not listening to me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.68,0:04:35.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're lucky the Restrictive Current\Nmade contact
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.12,0:04:36.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,with just the shield area.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:39.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If it had been\Nthe Six Flowers themselves,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,you'd be dead now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:43.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:47.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what?\NDon't be so hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.60,0:04:51.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As it turned out, thanks to Inoue,\Nwe came through without a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.01,0:04:55.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You do not understand\Nhow serious this is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-Is this the Soul Society?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:07.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This place is known as the Rukon District,\Nthe Drifting Spirit Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:17.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is where souls first live\Nupon coming to Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.36,0:05:21.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and is on the perimeter of Seireitei\Nwhere Soul Reapers live.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:24.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's the poorest place in Soul Society,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.16,0:05:25.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but also the freest,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:28.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,and has the largest population\Nof souls in Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.33,0:05:31.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… But for all that,\Nthere's no one around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.54,0:05:32.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:36.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?\NIt looks so different on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.09,0:05:38.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh that…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.37,0:05:42.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got it! That's where the Soul Reapers live…\Nthe Sei-whatever…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Awright!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.64,0:05:48.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You fool! Don't get too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:50.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.02,0:05:50.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.64,0:06:12.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:12.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:18.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,since someone tried to pass through\Nthe Seirei Gate without a travel permit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.60,0:06:23.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a rare guest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:26.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.45,0:06:35.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So the Ryoka have landed\Noutside the Seirei Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:39.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Since they're on that side,\Nthere's no need for us to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.85,0:06:43.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well… Especially since on that side…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:48.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanbo will be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.60,0:06:55.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now come at me from anywhere…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.60,0:06:56.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.47,0:07:01.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:05.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?!\NHe's too big to be human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:07.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just what is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.68,0:07:09.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Jidanbo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.30,0:07:14.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He was chosen from among\Nthe best in Soul Society
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.46,0:07:19.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to guard the White Road Gate,\None of the four gates of Seirei Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.67,0:07:25.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Guard? Which means we\Nhave to beat him to get inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:28.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But that won't be an easy task…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.35,0:07:32.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In the 300 years that\Nhe has been on duty,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:36.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,no one has been able to break\Nthrough the White Road Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:40.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is legendary for his power and strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.13,0:07:43.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So how do we fight a guy like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.09,0:07:46.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's where your intelligence comes in.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think, first, a meeting is in order\Nto come up with a strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.28,0:07:52.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ichigo…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:56.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chad! Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.44,0:07:59.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come back! Come back, both of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.43,0:08:02.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, wait…\NI'm coming to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.60,0:08:21.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.14,0:08:28.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.61,0:08:30.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You must be country bumpkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.09,0:08:34.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now listen up.\NWe have rules in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.09,0:08:38.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First, wash your hands when\Nyou return from outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:42.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two, don't eat food\Nthat's fallen on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.97,0:08:48.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three, when you fight,\Nit's one-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:55.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My first opponent will be that kid…\Nwith the candy hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.99,0:09:00.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You wait here quietly, until I'm done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.91,0:09:03.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:04.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.09,0:09:08.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait for my chance and\Nopen up a hole in this wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.09,0:09:12.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The instant I'm done, aim and\Nshoot your Tsubaki at him through the hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.95,0:09:14.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still scheming something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.27,0:09:19.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has surprisingly sharp ears…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:20.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.55,0:09:23.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Chad! Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.31,0:09:26.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! Are you all right?\NYou're not hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:29.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm alive and kicking!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait over there, we're…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.66,0:09:34.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,About that, Orihime…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.95,0:09:38.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you and Chad just stay put?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:38.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:42.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, Ichigo?\NThat's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.38,0:09:46.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Don't worry, just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.01,0:09:48.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Uryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.31,0:09:51.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our time is limited!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:56.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Instead of just you, we have to\Nattack together, and get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you're there, Ishida?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.93,0:10:00.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've been here all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:04.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit saying irritating things\Nat a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.30,0:10:05.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, will you all shut up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:12.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.32,0:10:14.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Probably?! What're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:13.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:15.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand the situation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.42,0:10:16.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cripes…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:19.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.21,0:10:21.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How can I not worry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you something interesting…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.41,0:10:29.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My Soul Reaper strength was\Nsupposed to be restored in ten full days.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.01,0:10:32.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I got it back in five.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.98,0:10:37.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So what do you think\NI did the remaining five days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.01,0:10:39.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What were you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.62,0:10:46.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fighting. For five days and nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:49.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I fought that hat-and-clogs guy…\None-on-one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.60,0:10:53.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it… You learned\Nthe secrets of fighting…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:54.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Nope…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:55.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:59.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't teach me a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:01.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stamina and guts…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I got 'em even if I didn't want 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:26.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you done talking?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.18,0:11:31.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember asking\Nyou to wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:38.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are a country bumpkin, after all.\NYou don't know your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.08,0:11:43.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When someone waits for you…\Nyou say, "thank you"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.35,0:11:48.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:11:58.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.06,0:12:08.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.43,0:12:14.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it bad manners to attack\Nbefore your opponent is ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.39,0:12:27.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.10,0:12:30.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He's laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.51,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're gutsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.51,0:12:38.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good! It's been decades since\Nsomeone stopped my thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.32,0:12:40.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right! This is great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.79,0:12:44.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Today, I get to give it\Neverything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:47.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Among those who tried to\Npass through here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:50.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,there have been only three,\Nincluding you,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.71,0:12:53.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who were able to stop my first thrust.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.49,0:13:00.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,However…not one has been\Nable to stop…my second thrust!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.41,0:13:12.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… Good, you're still standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna keep coming! Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:18.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanda Ten Strikes Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.45,0:13:20.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,One!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.81,0:13:22.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.89,0:13:25.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Four!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:26.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Five!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.19,0:13:29.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Six! Seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.98,0:13:31.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.24,0:13:34.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Seven! Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.45,0:13:37.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err…Six! Eight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:44.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's time for the finish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:06.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.10,0:14:26.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why…?!\NWhy are you…still standing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.10,0:14:29.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's standing!\NKurosaki is still standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:30.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:31.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.09,0:14:36.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What Ichigo learned from that guy\Nwas not about stamina or guts…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:38.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,or even the secrets of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.72,0:14:42.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Without a doubt, he has spiritual power\Nbeyond the norm of Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.25,0:14:48.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he's still clumsy at\Nwielding that power…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.31,0:14:53.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What he lacked when he confronted\Nother Soul Reapers…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.28,0:14:55.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,was experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:59.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And once he got that, he's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:01.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:04.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.51,0:15:07.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.68,0:15:12.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's gonna be so strong,\Nit'll be scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:20.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! Not yet!\NI'm not…finished yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.88,0:15:22.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Another axe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:38.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Try this! My final lethal attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:42.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Jidanda Banzai Strike Festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:51.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I'm gonna destroy those axes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.11,0:16:25.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:29.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That Kurosaki…\NWhat'd he just do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.41,0:16:32.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That giant…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.06,0:16:34.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,went flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.38,0:16:43.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hah! Man, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.09,0:16:48.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I slipped and fell on my butt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.14,0:16:51.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:56.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bet you think I went flying.\NHah! What're you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:17:01.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be blown away, never happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.40,0:17:04.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's why country bumpkins\Nare such a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:08.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, I'll use my axes again and…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.68,0:17:12.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Axes…?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:19.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm… Jidanbo's axes were\Ndestroyed in one blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.30,0:17:22.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Those giant axes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:27.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:33.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,M-My…axes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:33.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.64,0:17:38.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They're broken! They're broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My axes are…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,broken!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:50.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, he's crying.\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.98,0:17:52.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like a siren.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.90,0:17:59.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Er…hey…I'm sorry about this.\NFor breaking your axes…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.15,0:18:02.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have to break both of them,\NI know…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Bad of me…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:10.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're…not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.15,0:18:18.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You and I are enemies,\Nbut you're concerned for me, a loser…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.44,0:18:23.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a big heart…\NYou're really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.15,0:18:29.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err… Well, when someone cries that much,\Nanyone would want to console him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:35.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, I'm acting like\Na kid over mere axes…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:38.55,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an embarrassment as a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's… my loss!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:44.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:51.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A complete loss!\NAs a warrior…as a man…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:53.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I lost to you completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.09,0:18:58.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's been 300 years since I became\Nthe guard of the White Road Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:19:01.87,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've never once lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:06.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You are the first man to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.64,0:19:11.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:16.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I, Jidanbo, grant your permission\Nto pass through the White Road Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:17.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can all of us really pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:32.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I lost to your leader.\NI have no right to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.65,0:19:33.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.43,0:19:37.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kurosaki is our leader?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:40.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why're you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.09,0:19:43.72,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.09,0:19:50.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo, huh? That's a cute name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.97,0:19:54.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Ichi means "one" and\Ngo stands for "protect"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:54.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's not cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.89,0:19:58.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take care, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:03.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you are\Npassing through this gate…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:07.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But on the other side, they're all strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.50,0:20:14.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. As long as you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.53,0:20:18.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll open the gate so stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:24.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get scared.\NI'll give it one heave.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ohhh…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.96,0:20:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.16,0:20:53.93,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.73,0:20:56.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought that thing\Ncould be lifted…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:03.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NWhy're you standing there like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.21,0:21:05.34,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.09,0:21:22.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that…?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.66,0:21:27.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of Squad 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:29.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Gin Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:46.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.29,0:21:48.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:52.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.04,0:21:54.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.20,0:21:56.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.24,0:21:58.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:22:00.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.33,0:22:03.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I was casually walking through town
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.58,0:22:05.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Around the time dusk fell\Nand the city was bathed in red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.66,0:22:07.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It was an afternoon with\Ncrowds of people coming and going
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.87,0:22:09.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why but\NI just stood there and watched
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:12.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then my cell phone started to vibrate\Nand I made myself move
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.24,0:22:14.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,hoping it could fill\Nin this hole in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:16.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You’re not alone\NYou see, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:18.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta hold each other up
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.41,0:22:20.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With much appreciation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:23.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I send a rhapsody filled\Nwith treasured thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.08,0:22:26.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To the people who have\Nalways held me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.20,0:22:28.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:30.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.41,0:22:32.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever I may be
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:34.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll always be grateful for who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.79,0:22:37.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious wild boar gang attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The only one who can stop this\Noutrageous bunch is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.47,0:22:46.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I leave it to you, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.24,0:22:50.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Right! Pararira pararira...\NHey, don't run away, you guys!